    • Crop

      public Crop​(String name, int cost, int minutesToHarvest, int perUnitXP, Integer yield, int minYield, int maxYield, int salePrice)
      Creates a crop with specifed parameters including actual yield.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of crop.
      cost - The cost of crop.
      minutesToHarvest - The time for the crop to grow to maturity.
      perUnitXP - The experience points per unit of crop.
      yield - The actual yield of crop will be produced.
      minYield - The minimum yield of crop can be produced.
      maxYield - The maximum yield of crop can be produced.
      salePrice - The sale price of crop.

      public boolean equals​(Object o)
      Compares the specified object with this crop for equality. It returns true if and only if specified object is a crop and both crops have the same name, cost, time for the crop to grow to maturity, minimum yield, maximum yield and sale price.
